    <cardDescription>
      <Value><![CDATA[If you follow Maeve Bassett's guided tour of the W. J. Beal Botanical Garden's medicinal collections at Michigan State University, you'll learn facts about the lifesaving qualities of a G&T, the Doctrine of Signatures, and how psychedelic mushrooms advanced human cognition. To a group of phytochemists, these stories are the basis of our work and may well be the inspiration for some of us. ]]></Value>
